Class Marker

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.client.map.Marker
All Implemented Interfaces:
Shape
Direct Known Subclasses:
AlertMarker, BeaconMarker, CameraMarker, ControllerMarker, DmsMarker, GateArmMarker, IncidentMarker, LaneMarkingMarker, LcsMarker, MeterMarker, MonitorMarker, ParkingAreaMarker, ParkingMarker, PlanMarker, PlayListMarker, R_NodeMarker, RectMarker, TagReaderMarker, TimeMarker, TollingMarker, WayfindingMarker, WeatherSensorMarker
public abstract class Marker extends Object implements Shape
A marker which delegates Shape methods to a general path.
Author:
Douglas Lau
